e":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:20:43.000Z","msg":"醫護一罷分分鐘死人架喎 辭職咪算囉"},{"pid":"9d51388dd14287e6674ca91d8c6c13051cfc1fee","tid":1263631,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:34:38.000Z","msg":"佢哋根本冇可能罷工<br />\n咪撚戇鳩啦好嘛"},{"pid":"fb1cd75095ba01492a6eb81ca2658a6f554ea06f","tid":1263631,"uid":188482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04d612be9cd8105c9f99ae486dd20f78d92d8b53","tid":1263631,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:20:43.000Z","msg":"醫護一罷分分鐘死人架喎 辭職咪算囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:38:17.000Z","msg":"辭職盞比ha一個籍口運d支那豬落黎做"}]}